Class MethodPropertyDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.beans.FeatureDescriptor
      • java.beans.PropertyDescriptor
        • repast.simphony.ui.probe.MethodPropertyDescriptor
  • public class MethodPropertyDescriptor
extends PropertyDescriptor
    Property descriptor for properties that are accessed via methods. This extends PropertyDescriptor, adding support for converting to and from a String.
    Author:
    Nick Collier
